      "text": "We just sent them on back to the rear.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the Germans' defenses really started getting tough as we moved further into France and particularly when we hit the Vosges Mountains.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's a very mountainous area between-- runs along the German-French border in northern France.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And at that time, then, the fighting became very bitter and very expensive from there on, heavy casualties on both sides throughout the winter of '44 and '45.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
